reviewText: The only reason i got this film is for my collection now Rob zombie wrecked this film when he put a rape scene in it that is why i watch the theatrical version

I made a mistake in purchasing this movie, thinking it was the original "Halloween Movie". That's why i sent it back, but I cannot comment on it because I never watched it. Please don't take this the wrong way. I'm sure the movie is good, but it wasn't what I wanted.
